Package com.example.a50zo.model

Class GameModel

java.lang.Object
com.example.a50zo.model.GameModel
public class GameModel extends Object
Main game model that manages the game state, players, deck, and game logic. Implements the core rules of Cincuentazo.
Version:
1.0
Author:
